<div class="title">Bad Time For A Caffeine Addict</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine (Vivarin)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Bryan&Exact=1">Bryan</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Bryan. "Bad Time For A Caffeine Addict: An Experience with Caffeine (Vivarin) (exp6778)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 26, 2002. erowid.org/exp/6778</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
